894static uint16_T look1_iu16lu64n48_binlcse(uint16_T u0, const uint16_T bp0[],



895  const uint16_T table[], uint32_T maxIndex)



896{



897  uint16_T y;



898  uint64_T frac;



899  uint32_T iRght;



900  uint32_T iLeft;



901  uint32_T bpIdx;



902



903  /* Lookup 1-D



904     Search method: 'binary'



905     Use previous index: 'off'



906     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



907     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



908     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



909     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



910     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



911   */



912  /* Prelookup - Index and Fraction



913     Index Search method: 'binary'



914     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



915     Use previous index: 'off'



916     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



917     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



918     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



919   */



920  if (u0 <= bp0[0U]) {



921    iLeft = 0U;



922    frac = 0ULL;



923  } else if (u0 < bp0[maxIndex]) {



924    /* Binary Search */



925    bpIdx = maxIndex >> 1U;



926    iLeft = 0U;



927    iRght = maxIndex;



928    while (iRght - iLeft > 1U) {



929      if (u0 < bp0[bpIdx]) {



930        iRght = bpIdx;



931      } else {



932        iLeft = bpIdx;



933      }



934



935      bpIdx = (iRght + iLeft) >> 1U;



936    }



937



938    frac = ((uint64_T)(uint16_T)((uint32_T)u0 - bp0[iLeft]) << 48) / (uint16_T)



939      ((uint32_T)bp0[iLeft + 1U] - bp0[iLeft]);



940  } else {



941    iLeft = maxIndex - 1U;



942    frac = 281474976710656ULL;



943  }



944



945  /* Interpolation 1-D



946     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



947     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



948     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



949     Overflow mode: 'wrapping'



950   */



951  if (table[iLeft + 1U] >= table[iLeft]) {



952    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)(uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft + 1U]



953      - table[iLeft]) * frac) >> 48) + table[iLeft]);



954  } else {



955    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft] - (uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)



956      table[iLeft] - table[iLeft + 1U]) * frac) >> 48));



957  }



958



959  return y;



960}
